Jiangxi will train 10,000 rural primary school music and beauty teachers within 3 years-Xinhuanet Xinhua Agency, Nanchang, May 22(Reporter Chen Yushan) Reporters recently learned from the Jiangxi Province Department of Education that in order to enhance the support capacity of teachers in short supply and realize the balanced development of rural compulsory education, Jiangxi Province plans to use three years to provide rural areas in the province since 2016.(Township and below) Each primary school training qualified music, art, physical education teachers each one, a total of 10,000. It is understood that the training object for Jiangxi Province 's rural primary schools under the age of 45 with music, art, physical education subject knowledge or talent, can concurrently music, art, physical education curriculum teachers of other subjects. Through training, so that they master the basic knowledge and teaching skills of music, art, physical education subject teaching, update teaching ideas and concepts, master modern teaching methods,To improve the ability of subject teaching, activity design, campus culture and self-development, build a team of music and sports teachers with one specialty and many abilities, and alleviate the problem of lack of music and sports teachers in rural areas.(City, district) primary school music, fine arts, sports training 1, a total of 300 trainers, comprehensively improve their teaching demonstration leading ability, teaching and research activity design organization ability, training ability, network research workshop construction ability, play the role of teaching, demonstration, guidance and supervision.
